title: Rugby Union Six Nations - Scotland v Italy - 2015.02.28 - 504p x
description:
SPORT: Six Nations Rugby Union - Scotland v Italy
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Saturday 28th February 2015 
Time: 14:00 to 16:30 

John Inverdale introduces live coverage as Scotland face Italy at Murrayfield in the third round of fixtures in this year's Six Nations. The hosts will be aiming for three in a row against the Azzurri after last season's thrilling victory in Rome, which came courtesy of Duncan Weir's last-minute drop goal. That win ended Scotland's run of eight consecutive away defeats in the Six Nations and ensured they finished above Italy in the table. Studio guests include former Scotland player and coach Sir Ian McGeechan, Chris Paterson and Carlo del Fava, while match commentary comes from Eddie Butler and Andy Nicol. This is the full BBC coverage.
